highlights.description: My librarian asked me if I was related to Osama bin Laden
Professors targeting me because I am a student of color
The last time I went out in Madison the security guard pushed us out
Going out to celebrate but instead getting called a racial slur
Waiting for a bus late at night and being threatened with "that kid looks like he's a Muslim"
What we really want is funding, power, spaces to call our own, curriculum that addresses those things
LVN: I'm excited that there is a project like that helps humanize us
